==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nonunion
<hw>Non*un"ion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
belonging to, or affiliated with, a trades union; <as>as, a
<ex>nonunion</ex> carpenter</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not employing trade union members; not recognizing
or favoring trades unions or trades-unionists; <as>as, a
<ex>nonunion</ex> contractor; a <ex>nonunion</ex>
subcontractor</as>.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Non*un"ion*ism</wf>
<pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nonunionist</ent>⟦br⟧
